  "body": "# Problem\n\nWe want to mention in [this banner](https://www.figma.com/file/dEIljL7UPbXgsZUA0Q4qlE5E/Onboarding), with minimal words, that a user's contact code will also change in v1.\n\n## Implementation\n\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15470435/64116238-ae4ce780-cd89-11e9-9af0-fdfed4722d3c.png\" width=200/>\n\n\nChange this line from:\n\n`Updating to 1.0 will result in a loss of access to this wallet.`\n\nto\n\n`Your contact details will change as well.`\n\nWe're justifying replacing the original line because it's not strictly true. A user who updates to v1 without his/her seed phrase will lose access to their wallet -in- Status on -that device- only.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\nCopy change matches exactly.",
